<members name="Snake">
<Apple>
<summary> 
This class randomly generates an <c>Apple</c> for the game Snake.
</summary>
<returns>
A new <c>Apple</c> at a randomly generated location in the game area.
</returns>
<param name="map"> 
A matrix <c>char[,]</c> that details the board layout, any other Apples already on the board, and (optional) the <c>Snake</c> head or body. The new apple will only be placed in an empty location on this board.
</param>
<param name="seed"> 
An integer to help when creating multiple Apples at once. Leave as 0 if only creating a single Apple in a short timeframe. 
</param>
</Apple>
<X>
<value>
Gets the X coordinate of the <c>Apple</c>.
</value>
</X>
<Y>
<value>
Gets the Y coordinate of the <c>Apple</c>.
</value>
</Y>
<Location>
<value>
Gets the coordinate pair of the location of the <c>Apple</c>.
</value>
</Location>
